    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/b96cc742e2758fc888fa6b9dfd43a26a.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>当一切黑暗散尽</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>当残页指引前方</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>你是否愿意和我一起</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>再次奏响那 梦中的弦音？</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/5c6c1078f2184888e86232cc995520cd.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个寂静的雨夜，少女<strong>夕时音</strong>为了寻找传说中的“奇迹之草”，踏入山中禁地后神秘失踪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年<strong>秋忆轩</strong>循着回忆与线索，深入机关重重的洞窟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尸体、怪物、谎言与旧日温暖交织，真相在黑暗深处渐渐浮现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/fbe2847edf55d6c502133f5b962e0dbc.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏包含丰富的故事分支与多个结局，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带你穿越童话与现实的缝隙，见证希望与失落交织的命运终曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/fcd6bf3d53946ed2dc0a2e3be87b2cd1.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/db7a9f46924ad267c9c97f86100777c0.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动人细腻的叙事体验</strong><br>故事承接《羽翼的祈愿》世界观，讲述少女与少年的命运纠葛，深刻触动玩家内心。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>细腻恐怖的氛围营造</strong><br>游戏塑造出令人毛骨悚然又耐人寻味的环境，每个角落都潜藏未知恐惧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创意丰富的机关谜题</strong><br>机关与线索环环相扣，谜题设计灵巧且紧扣剧情，难度适中，注重引导与思考。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精致细腻的画面表现</strong><br>画面精美细腻，关键情节配以精致CG，增强沉浸体验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/b4adb91085013bd359fa93150ef8b35d.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏类型：</strong>恐怖解谜   <br><strong>结局数目：</strong>4个（*以及部分隐藏结局）    <br><strong>通关预计时间：</strong>3~5小时</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <br><strong>基本按键：</strong>   <br>移动：方向键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查/确认：Z/空格/回车</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菜单/取消：X/ESC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存档管理：F5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑步：Shift</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/d482d2ad000ba86eec93c1a3965cc6bb.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=120 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏作者：秋之忧郁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏画师：雨兮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宣传图画师：星羽樱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏发行：梦结界工作室</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~更多Staff请见游戏内名单~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264350/extras/2ede77ab68b6008fc08f3d7931967a78.avif?t=1755316168\" width=610 height=120 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎玩家进行实况和创作同人作品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏谜题难度适中，建议尽量避免查看攻略哦~</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的剧本、角色设定、立绘及人物CG均为原创作品，请勿私自拆包或二次发布。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如有任何问题，欢迎随时联系作者。尽量会在第一时间回复并解决大家在游戏中出现的问题~<br><a href=\"mailto:反馈邮箱：413228337@qq.com\">反馈邮箱：413228337@qq.com</a></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后祝大家游戏愉快~！！！   </p></li></ul>",
